rdf:Description.machine:description: This minimalist illustration features three stylized coffee beans in a warm, earthy brown color. The beans are accompanied by small, delicate floral elements, adding a touch of elegance and freshness. The simple, clean lines and the use of a single color palette make this image perfect for branding materials, especially for coffee shops or organic product lines.
rdf:Description.machine:shortdescription: Minimalist illustration of three coffee beans with floral elements in earthy brown tones.
